Text: Foz TripSusan How have you been I just got the final prices for your Foz trip Its R total and with todays exchange its around US I just wanted to confirm this is still a YES before I pay today This price includes flight from Rio to Iguau flight from Iguau to SP transfers to and from airport nights stay breakfast both mornings english speaking guide for both days tour of falls on both sides Brasil and Argentina boat tour at bottom of falls tour of the bird aviary Ill wait to hear from youJan
